- Login with attempt handling.

âœ… **Activity Tracking**

- Log 6 activity types:
  - ğŸš¶ Walking (steps, distance)
  - ğŸŠ Swimming (laps, heart rate)
  - ğŸƒ Running (distance, elevation)
  - ğŸš´ Cycling (distance, speed)
  - ğŸ§˜ Yoga (duration, style)
  - ğŸ’ª Weightlifting (sets, reps)

âœ… **Goal Monitoring**

- Set daily calorie goals.
- Track progress with real-time calculations.

âœ… **Validation**

- Reject invalid inputs (negative numbers, incorrect formats).

